Zhenyuan 3D Sleeping Eye Mask with Cotton Shading Memory Foam for Comfort & Travel

Enjoy deeper, undisturbed rest with the Zhenyuan 3D Sleeping Eye Mask. Designed with rebound memory foam and soft cotton shading, this mask blocks out light completely while ensuring maximum comfort for your eyes.

Its 3D ergonomic design prevents pressure on the eyelids, making it ideal for sleep, travel, yoga, or relaxation. Available in black, gray, and pink, the mask offers breathable comfort and long-lasting wear.

How to Use:

  1. Place the mask gently over your eyes.

  2. Adjust the elastic strap for a secure fit.

  3. Relax and enjoy full blackout shading for quality rest.

Specifications:

  • Available Colors: Black, Gray, Pink

  • Function: 3D shading blackout design

  • Material: Rebound memory foam & cotton

  • Style: 3D ergonomic comfort

  • Lightweight & portable

Why You’ll Love It:
✔ Provides full blackout shading
✔ Pressure-free 3D design for eyelids
✔ Soft rebound memory foam comfort
✔ Lightweight & travel-friendly
✔ Perfect for sleep, meditation, and relaxation

Package Contents:
1 × Zhenyuan 3D Sleeping Eye Mask
